		sc_substatus int,

		sc_bytes int,
		cs_bytes int,
		s_timetaken int

	AS
	BEGIN

		@result = EXTRACT
			s_date DateTime,
			s_time string,
			s_sitename string,
			cs_method string,
			cs_uristem string,

			cs_cookie string,
			cs_referer string,

	RETURN;

	AS 
		SELECT * FROM 
		(
			VALUES(1,2),(2,4)
		) 
	AS 
	T(a, b);
	CREATE PROCEDURE onesdk1264.dbo.onesdk6043()
	AS BEGIN
	  CREATE VIEW onesdk1264.dbo.onesdk8903 
	  AS

}
